<plot>"LITTLE BONES" is a short film about a studious Latino boy who is woken up late at night by his father, a former gangster with a broken leg and a hidden agenda. Soon, the kid finds himself on a quest through the streets of East Los Angeles to buy a carton of cigarettes for his menacing father - but without the necessary funds to buy them! Relying solely on his wits, charisma and street smarts, the boy shows us just how resourceful one has to be to survive in the rough barrios of LA.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?337904</url></doc>
